\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
S_{\mathrm{eff}}\left[\phi,\sigma\right]=\frac{1}{2}\phi_{a}\left(-\square-m^{2}\right)\phi_{a}+J_{a}\phi_{a}+\frac{3}{2\lambda}\sigma^{2}-\frac{1}{2}\sigma\phi_{a}\phi_{a},
\end{equation}

\end_inset

which is now quadratic in the 
\begin_inset Formula $\phi_{a}$
\end_inset

